{"tid":550261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲細路咁嘅","createTime":"2018-02-04T15:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T15:31:54.000Z","uid":149563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8b89c952f24f82df7503d97eeee211a9ae8e36","tid":550261,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"有次排隊等食飯<br />\n聽到個細路同佢老母講<br />\n👩🏼：老母<br />\n👶🏼：細路<br />\n<br />\n👩🏼：你啱啱去咗邊度玩啊，而家先返嚟，排到我哋啦<br />\n<br />\n👶🏼：我唔係去玩啊，我去咗睇補充練習啊。你比我做嗰啲我已經做晒啦，我覺得唔夠想再買多幾本啊<br />\n<br />\n係唔係而家啲細路都咁假，扮乖扮老積希望老豆老母鍾意<br />\n但係我啲朋友又話可能依家啲細路真係咁呢，日日掛住做功課搞到佢哋咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27b09b9f4832c55ce8ea62c2fad961968a2f299","tid":550261,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"冇咩問題，可能真係睇，你撚知咩<br />\n細路勤力唔好咩"},{"pid":"dff7763b43a295b3c2794100120a5880e382031a","tid":550261,"uid":73909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"係唔係想問屋企攞錢買補充然後自己食咗啲錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f223a049dfcde043e6653b9947abd91ecc71ee","tid":550261,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"可能做完有獎<br />\n所以做多幾本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}